<li>Dunston Road (canal scene), <a href="/wiki/London" title="London">London</a> <a href="/wiki/E_postcode_area" title="E postcode area">E2</a></li>
<li>10 Gwynne Park Avenue (Barbara and John's house), <a href="/wiki/Woodford_Bridge" title="Woodford Bridge">Woodford Bridge</a>, <a href="/wiki/London" title="London">London</a> IG8 8AB</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Trafalgar_Square" title="Trafalgar Square">Trafalgar Square</a>, London</li>
